Parameter functions¶

In [71]:
def add(a,b):
    return 1+((1/120)*(a+b))

def con(u,v):
    return (0*(u)*(v))+0.3

def sp(u,v):
    return 1+1/3240*(36-(6-u/2)**2)*(36-(6-v/2)**2)

def med(u,v):
    B = np.zeros((25,25))
    for i in range(25):
        for j in range(25):
            
            if u[i][j]<=8:
                B[i][j]=0.2
            elif u[i][j]>17:
                B[i][j]=0.7
            else:
                B[i][j]=0.5
    return B
